# Types templates (from `types.json`)

Summarizes **430** files: **`**/types/**`**, **`*.type.ts`**, **`*.guardz.ts`** (see [`.agents/file-lists/types.json`](../file-lists/types.json)). Strict typing, **`readonly`** on DTO fields; **`any` forbidden** (**`rules-bundle-core.mdc`**).

## Inventory snapshot

| Fact | Typical value |
| --- | --- |
