## Template — DTO `interface`

```typescript
import type { Nullable } from "guardz";

import type { KeyDTO } from "types/KeyDTO/KeyDTO.type";

export interface ExampleDTO {
  readonly id: string;
  readonly name: Nullable<string>;
  readonly key: KeyDTO;
}
```

## Guardz

- Files ending in **`.guardz.ts`** hold runtime validators / guards; align with **`guardz`** usage elsewhere in the feature.

## Immutability files

- **Do not** modify files whose names contain **`DTO`** or **`RequestParams`** in ways that violate immutable-file rules (**`rules-bundle-core.mdc`**, **`pnpm run cursor:verify`**).

